data.description: Welcome home! Home offers 3 bedrooms with 2 full baths, sitting on a dead end street with fencing to keep your kids and pets safe in the yard. Workshop/Garage quite large to accommodate all your storage needs. Home is pet friendly with doggie doors throughout the home. Also, offering your choice of a second living area or a game room! Stay warm and cozy each winter with a wood burning fireplace! New windows with some being picture windows for the natural sunlight throughout the home! A/C Central units being 2 and 5 years old. Home is wired and connected to city gas for a generac to be placed. Last but not least fresh grass has been planted to soon be full and green again!! Call today for personal showing to see what all this home truly offers!
